Sentencas: Composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (GDC) are investigated to assess for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) applications at relatively low operating temperatures (650-800 degrees C).
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: LSCF with a high surface area of 55 m(2)g(-1) is synthesized via a complex method involving inorganic nano-dispersants.
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The fuel cell performances of anode-supported SOFCs are characterized as a function of compositions of GDC with a surface area of 5 m(2)g(-1).
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SOFCs consist of the following: LSCF-GDC composites as a cathode, GDC as an interlayer, yttrium stabilized zirconia (YSZ) as an electrolyte, Ni-YSZ (50: 50 wt%) as an anode functional layer, and Ni-YSZ (50: 50 wt%) for support.
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cathodes are prepared for 6LSCF-4GDC (60 : 40 wt%), 5LSCF-5GDC (50 : 50 wt%), and 4LSCF-6GDC (40: 60 wt%).
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The 5LSCF-5GDC cathode shows 1.29 Wcm(-2), 0.97 Wcm(-2), and 0.47 Wcm(-2) at 780 degrees C, 730 degrees C, and 680 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The 6LSCF-4GDC shows 0.92 Wcm(-2), 0.71 Wcm(-2), and 0.54 Wcm(-2) at 780 degrees C, 730 degrees C, and 680 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 780 degrees C, the highest fuel cell performance is achieved by the 5LSCF-5GDC, while at 680 degrees C the 6LSCF-4GDC shows the highest performance.
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The best composition of the porous composite cathodes with LSCF (55 m(2)g(-1)) and GDC (5 m(2)g(-1)) needs to be considered with a function of temperature.
Titulo: Characterizations of composite cathodes with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 for solid oxide fuel cells
